# Seva AI — Global Git Ignore

# System Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp

# Environment Secrets (Crucial)
.env
.env.local
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/firebase-applet-config.json

# Node.js
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Build artifacts
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.firebase/

# IDEs
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# Service Accounts
**/*service-account.json
**/credentials.json
